text: Patrice Debray (born 25 January 1951) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Haute-Saône department,http://www.assemblee- nationale.fr/13/tribun/fiches_id/267309.asp and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Politicians from Bourgogne-Franche-Comté Category:French physicians Category:People from Neuerburg
